  <bodyText><![CDATA[<p><img src="/media/13093706/whistler-powder-skiing-838x350.jpg" alt="besttimetoski" data-udi="umb://media/5ef46cbbe9ef41e8b0261a22851b7552" /></p>
<p><strong>Whether you’re a thrill-seeker or gentle meandering - we can help you find the right time to hit the slopes to suit you. </strong></p>
<p>We are here to ensure that on your next ski holiday, you can enjoy that breath of fresh air, get your heart racing and your body soaring whilst you make the most of the great outdoors and all that alpine-life has to offer. </p>
<p><em>See what's new for Inghams ski holidays on our<span> </span><a data-udi="umb://document/4323a332132044fba8041dc874c3bc85" href="/ski-holidays/whats-new-on-the-slopes" title="What's new on the slopes">What's new on the slopes</a><span> </span>page for all the latest on new resorts, offers, accommodation and more.</em><span> </span></p>
<h2 style="text-align: center;">Best months to ski</h2>
<p>With a fantastic long ski season across Europe and Canada, there are so many opportunities to take a great ski or snowboard holiday. To help you decide when to go, we have put together some highlights per month:</p>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-6">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow u-text-center">
<h2><a data-udi="umb://document/435446b0b8bb4556bd48e1afbbe32338" href="/{localLink:umb://document/435446b0b8bb4556bd48e1afbbe32338}" title="January skiing">January ski holidays</a></h2>
<p><img src="/media/13095357/january-new-size.jpg" alt="" data-udi="umb://media/5ca5a4fa2fed462e8f9a5bd974389e8e" /></p>
<p>What better way to get rid of the January-blues then to book yourself a skiing or snowboarding holiday. Take yourself off for a fun-packed and quiet, queue free piste week away out on the snowy slopes of Europe or Canada. </p>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/435446b0b8bb4556bd48e1afbbe32338" href="/{localLink:umb://document/435446b0b8bb4556bd48e1afbbe32338}" class="c-btn">View January</a></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-6">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow u-text-center">
<h2><a data-udi="umb://document/fbe98b0631fa4ed388a302e2fd6d0a58" href="/{localLink:umb://document/fbe98b0631fa4ed388a302e2fd6d0a58}" title="February skiing">February ski holidays</a></h2>
<p><img src="/media/13095349/february-new-size.jpg" alt="" data-udi="umb://media/0f61641af59540a094a78c6f5275a11b" /></p>
<p>The weather has slightly warmed and the days have grown longer meaning February is a great time to make the most of the slopes and head out for a ski trip, ideally during half-term for a family fun-filled week with the children.  </p>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/fbe98b0631fa4ed388a302e2fd6d0a58" href="/{localLink:umb://document/fbe98b0631fa4ed388a302e2fd6d0a58}" class="c-btn">View February</a></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-6">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow u-text-center">
<h2><a data-udi="umb://document/fd1b0716859547b3a92dd8cbbbe09a14" href="/{localLink:umb://document/fd1b0716859547b3a92dd8cbbbe09a14}" title="March skiing">March ski holidays</a></h2>
<p><img src="/media/13095351/march-new-size.jpg" alt="" data-udi="umb://media/640057f0a5134247ba42b999af6a6e29" /></p>
<p>By March the sun is usually shining stronger and the snow is deep, making it the perfect time of year to slip on yours skis (or snowboard) and enjoy the start of spring out on the mountains. </p>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/fd1b0716859547b3a92dd8cbbbe09a14" href="/{localLink:umb://document/fd1b0716859547b3a92dd8cbbbe09a14}" title="March skiing" class="c-btn">View March</a></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-6">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow u-text-center">
<h2><a data-udi="umb://document/93732bc5591f4b27b12da3503c02b7c3" href="/{localLink:umb://document/93732bc5591f4b27b12da3503c02b7c3}" title="April skiing">April ski holidays</a></h2>
<p><img src="/media/13095356/april-new-size.jpg" alt="" data-udi="umb://media/678bbe9f1b7d4539a2456f28a778cb98" /></p>
<p>Welcoming in the longer and brighter days and the joys of Easter, heading out to ski towards the end of the season is fantastic - make the most of being in resort at this time of year with outdoor cafes and après ski.</p>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/93732bc5591f4b27b12da3503c02b7c3" href="/{localLink:umb://document/93732bc5591f4b27b12da3503c02b7c3}" class="c-btn">View April</a></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-6">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow u-text-center">
<h2><a data-udi="umb://document/2819c143bbf84221b5e0a691e8b36bca" href="/{localLink:umb://document/2819c143bbf84221b5e0a691e8b36bca}" title="November skiing">November ski holidays</a></h2>
<p><img src="/media/13099901/skiier-snow-370x250.jpg" alt="NovemberSkiResorts" data-udi="umb://media/804c3343f5a044a3a037aca281543a22" /></p>
<p>It may seem early in the ski season to be heading out on the slopes, however with our resorts in Lapland, close to the Arctic Circle, where the snow settles nearly all year round, it's a great opportunity to get ahead of the rest. </p>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/2819c143bbf84221b5e0a691e8b36bca" href="/{localLink:umb://document/2819c143bbf84221b5e0a691e8b36bca}" class="c-btn">View November</a></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-6">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow u-text-center">
<h2><a data-udi="umb://document/8367ad97550248b1be0a9662df02fdfd" href="/{localLink:umb://document/8367ad97550248b1be0a9662df02fdfd}" title="December Skiing">December ski holidays</a></h2>
<p><img src="/media/13099992/christmas-guide-370x250.jpg" alt="DecemberSkiResorts" data-udi="umb://media/e4aa3bbc75444f5fa134073b48b2aac1" /></p>
<p>A wonderfully festive time of year to be away on a skiing holiday, in a resort surrounded by Christmas decorations and lively markets. With plenty of resorts offering fantastic snow conditions at this time of year, it is the perfect winter escape. </p>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/8367ad97550248b1be0a9662df02fdfd" href="/{localLink:umb://document/8367ad97550248b1be0a9662df02fdfd}" class="c-btn">View December</a></p>
</div>
</div>
<p> </p>
<h2 style="text-align: center;">Best time of year to ski</h2>
<p>If you want to make your ski trip extra special, then we are here to help and have put together some particularly celebratory times to go on your next skiing adventure: </p>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-6">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow u-text-center">
<h2><a data-udi="umb://document/94e3f609bee24db59a4918a0c66f8dee" href="/{localLink:umb://document/94e3f609bee24db59a4918a0c66f8dee}" title="Christmas Skiing">Christmas ski holidays</a></h2>
<p><img src="/media/13095359/christmas-new-size.jpg" alt="" data-udi="umb://media/bd2fbb249a40487ea02a1de90512dff3" /></p>
<p>Enjoy a festive getaway on a ski holiday at Christmas time. With plenty of skiing plus Christmas tipples and meals topped off with a Christmas cracker. Enjoy the local Christmas markets, the glowing Christmas tree lights and the festive atmosphere.</p>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/94e3f609bee24db59a4918a0c66f8dee" href="/{localLink:umb://document/94e3f609bee24db59a4918a0c66f8dee}" class="c-btn">View Christmas</a></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-6">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow u-text-center">
<h2><a data-udi="umb://document/e160fd915c794359a9625dc3263f8ce8" href="/{localLink:umb://document/e160fd915c794359a9625dc3263f8ce8}" title="New Year Skiing">New Year ski holidays</a></h2>
<p><img src="/media/13095360/new-year-new-size.jpg" alt="" data-udi="umb://media/0b7e12594eff42fda7308e8aac7e74b6" /></p>
<p>Après ski and more. Join in with the resort celebrations and welcome in the new year out on the slopes. Where better to enjoy the fun and parties then a snowy destination to feel the true magic and fun of New Years Eve. </p>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/e160fd915c794359a9625dc3263f8ce8" href="/{localLink:umb://document/e160fd915c794359a9625dc3263f8ce8}" class="c-btn">View New Years Eve</a></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-6">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow u-text-center">
<h2><a data-udi="umb://document/5cafb4722ba54fe9acbeb514514e8354" href="/{localLink:umb://document/5cafb4722ba54fe9acbeb514514e8354}" title="Easter Skiing">Easter ski holidays</a></h2>
<p><img src="/media/13095361/easter-new-size.jpg" alt="" data-udi="umb://media/7293110f2ec54c07a74d79a1188594fe" /></p>
<p>Make the most of the great outdoors and take your family for some quality time of skiing fun and outdoor activities. Be it joining a ski school, messing around in the snow park or having a go at sledding, there are great memories to be made. </p>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/5cafb4722ba54fe9acbeb514514e8354" href="/{localLink:umb://document/5cafb4722ba54fe9acbeb514514e8354}" class="c-btn">View Easter</a></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-6">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow u-text-center">
<h2><a data-udi="umb://document/7d4f46abfb6a4bc999ea4fcfc363cdf0" href="/{localLink:umb://document/7d4f46abfb6a4bc999ea4fcfc363cdf0}" title="Half-Term skiing">Half-Term ski holidays</a></h2>
<p><img src="/media/13095362/half-term-new-size.jpg" alt="" data-udi="umb://media/f6020e237f7947499047bf8638c117f7" /></p>
<p>Don't miss the opportunity to get together with friends and family and enjoy all that a skiing holiday has to offer. Book ski schools for the children and make the most of those lift passes as you enjoy a half-term ski holiday as a family. </p>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/7d4f46abfb6a4bc999ea4fcfc363cdf0" href="/{localLink:umb://document/7d4f46abfb6a4bc999ea4fcfc363cdf0}" class="c-btn">View Half-term</a></p>
</div>
</div>
<p> </p>
<div class="row">
<div class="col-md-12">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-grey c-card--generic-shadow ">
<div class="c-card_content c-section u-margin-top u-margin-bottom u-margin-left u-margin-right">
