<p style="text-align: center;"><span>Simply give us a call to book your holiday. Flights, hotel and transport? We’ve got you covered. </span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="tel:01483791111" class="InfinityNumber c-btn">Call us to book today</a></p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>]]></bodyText>
